{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-10-25","name":"Isabel Comyn","nameForms":[{"lang":"en","fullText":"Isabel Comyn","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Isabel"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"Comyn"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"alternateName":"Isobel Comyn","gender":"Female","lifespan":"1275–1335","fullLifespan":"about 1275–1335","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/5ulwj/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-904-88990-4-60/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/80525115","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-904-88990-4-60/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-904-88990-4-60/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1275","birthPlace":{"address":"Scotland","geo":{"latitude":56.81674,"longitude":-4.18396,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"deathDate":"+1335","deathPlace":{"address":"Scotland","geo":{"latitude":56.81674,"longitude":-4.18396,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"burialDate":"+1335","burialPlace":{"address":"Scotland","geo":{"latitude":56.81674,"longitude":-4.18396,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":"«b»Disputed Parentage«/b»\nScots Peerage, Vol. 2, p 258 under Comyn of Buchan, states that John Comyn had no issue by his wife, Isabel daughter of Duncan (McDuff) Earl of Fife.\n\nIt does not say that Isabel, daughter of Duncan, had no children, but there is no mention of any other spouse. The Wikitree article for Isabel, daughter of Duncan, mentions no daughters. This profile has been disconnected from her and her husband John Comyn. Complete Peerage, Vol. 2 p 375 says John Comyn died \"s.p.m.\" which means without male children. Neither it nor Scots Peerage say that he had no daughters by other women.\n\n«b»Biography of Isabel Comyn«/b»\nBirth: ABT 1297 in Buchan, Aberdeenshire, Scotland\nFather: John Comyn 3rd Earl of Buchan b: ABT 1242 in Buchan, Aberdeenshire, Scotland\nMother: Isabel MacDuff b: ABT 1280 in Methil, Fifeshire, Scotland\n\nMarriage 1 Freskin Frances le Cheyne b: ABT 1280 in Straloch, Pethshire, Scotland\n\n«b»Children«/b»\nReginald le Cheyne 3rd Laird of Straloch b: ABT 1330 in Straloch, Pethshire, Scotland\n\n«b»Research Notes«/b»\nIsabel's entered birthdate of 1279 has been removed, as a cursory review of the literature does not suggest a date of birth. Instead, her birthdate has been estimated as occurring around 1258, based on her daughter Christian Cheyne Seton's carefully estimated birthdate of 1279. Further research is needed to either determine her actual date of birth or a more informed estimation.","events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1275","date":"about 1275","place":"Scotland"},{"name":"Marriage","sources":"0","year":"1290","date":"about 1290","place":"Scotland","type":"Spousal","age":"15","id":"LY3D-28W"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1292","date":"about 1292","place":"Straloch, Perthshire, Scotland","age":"17","id":"GDT5-TMS"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1301","date":"1301","place":"Scotland","age":"26","id":"GVLS-XVZ"},{"name":"Death of Parent","sources":"0","year":"1305","date":"1305","place":"New Street, Spring Gardens, England","age":"30","id":"G212-KXP"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1335","date":"1335","place":"Scotland","age":"60"},{"name":"Burial","sources":"0","year":"1335","date":"1335","place":"Scotland","age":"60"}],"parent":[{"name":"Alasdair Comyn","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1260–1305","birthDate":"+1260","deathDate":"+1305","age":45,"@type":"Person","identifier":"G212-KXP","url":"https://ancestors.familysearch.org/en/G212-KXP/alasdair-comyn-1260-1305","publish